===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|yestreen}}, alteration of {{m|enm|yestereven|t=last night, yesterday evening}}, from {{inh|en|ang|ġiestranǣfen|t=yesterday evening}}, equivalent to {{af|en|yester-|e'en|t2=evening}}. Cognate with {{cog|fy|justerjûn|t=yestreen; last night}}.
